OL,3,CLake District road reopens following 8
OL,4,Cmonths of repairs
OL,6,FPeople can once again drive on the
OL,7,FKirkstone Pass, which has been closed
OL,8,Ffor eight months, while work took
OL,9,Fplace to repair damage caused by a
OL,10,Flandslip.
OL,12,FHeavy rainfall caused a landslide that
OL,13,Fpartly undermined the carriageway in
OL,14,FNovember 2025, leading to an emergency
OL,15,Froad closure.
OL,17,FThe landslide happened at High
OL,18,FKingate, halfway between Troutbeck and
OL,19,Fthe Kirkstone Inn, just before the
OL,20,Fstart of the Kirkstone Pass itself.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
