OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1784297953
OL,3,CLake District road reopens following 8
OL,4,Cmonths of repairs
OL,6,FThe repair has involved reinstating
OL,7,Fthe steep hillside and rebuilding the
OL,8,Fcarriageway and retaining wall. Expert
OL,9,Fground investigation teams were
OL,10,Fbrought in with work starting before
OL,11,FChristmas on surveys and determining
OL,12,Fthe best repair. The ground had to be
OL,13,Fstabilised and water diverted away to
OL,14,Fprevent further collapse.
OL,16,FThe council says it has been a complex
OL,17,Ffix. It means the road is now fully
OL,18,Fopen for the start of the main school
OL,19,Fholidays in one of the Lake District's
OL,20,Fbusiest locations.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
